<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>스콧 베센트 | 매크로렌즈 인물사전</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700&family=Noto+Serif+KR:wght@400;700;900&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --gold: #C4A35A;
    --gold-light: #e0c07a;
    --red: #C0392B;
    --ink: #0a0a0a;
    --ink-mid: #141414;
    --ink-soft: #1e1e1e;
    --line: rgba(196,163,90,.18);
    --text: #e8e0d0;
    --text-dim: rgba(232,224,208,.55);
    --text-muted: rgba(232,224,208,.35);
    --green: #27ae60;
    --blue: #2980b9;
  }

  * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  header {
    position: relative;
    padding: 64px 40px 52px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  header::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 100% 0%, rgba(196,163,90,.10) 0%, transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 0% 100%, rgba(41,128,185,.07) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }
  .header-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; display: flex; gap: 48px; align-items: flex-start; }

  .header-portrait {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 140px;
  }
  .portrait-frame {
    width: 140px; height: 175px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a140a, #0f0f0f);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 64px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .portrait-frame::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 60%, rgba(10,10,10,.8));
  }
  .portrait-label {
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    text-align: center; letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .header-content { flex: 1; }

  .brand-row {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .brand-dot { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gold); }
  .brand-name { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--gold); text-transform: uppercase; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; }
  .series-badge {
    margin-left: auto;
    background: rgba(196,163,90,.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196,163,90,.3);
    border-radius: 20px; padding: 3px 12px;
    font-size: 10px; color: var(--gold);
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -1px; color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .name-en {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 3px; margin-bottom: 18px;
    display: block;
  }
  .header-sub { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.8; max-width: 560px; }

  /* ── KEY STATS ── */
  .keystats {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0;
    margin-top: 28px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ks-item {
    flex: 1; min-width: 120px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--line);
    background: rgba(196,163,90,.03);
  }
  .ks-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .ks-label { font-size: 9px; color: var(--text-muted); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; margin-bottom: 5px; }
  .ks-val { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--gold-light); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    background: var(--ink-mid);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
  }
  .nav-inner {
    max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex; gap: 2px; padding: 0 40px;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  .nav-tab {
    color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500;
    padding: 13px 16px; cursor: pointer;
    border: none; background: none;
    white-space: nowrap; text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block; transition: color .2s;
    letter-spacing: .3px;
  }
  .nav-tab:hover { color: var(--text); }
  .nav-tab.active { color: var(--gold); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--gold); }

  /* ── MAIN ── */
  main { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px 80px; }

  /* ── SECTION ── */
  .section { margin-top: 60px; }
  .section-header {
    display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 28px; padding-bottom: 18px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .section-num {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1px; padding-top: 4px; flex-shrink: 0; opacity: .7;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.2vw, 22px);
    font-weight: 700; color: #fff; line-height: 1.35;
  }
  .section-title small {
    display: block;
    font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: 400;
    margin-top: 4px; letter-spacing: .3px;
  }

  /* ── PROSE ── */
  .prose { color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.95; font-size: 14.5px; }
  .prose + .prose { margin-top: 14px; }
  .prose strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; }
  .prose em { color: var(--gold-light); font-style: normal; }

  /* ── TIMELINE ── */
  .timeline { position: relative; padding-left: 32px; margin-top: 8px; }
  .timeline::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 8px; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 2px; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), rgba(196,163,90,.1)); }
  .tl-item { position: relative; margin-bottom: 36px; }
  .tl-dot {
    position: absolute; left: -28px; top: 5px;
    width: 14px; height: 14px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--ink); border: 2px solid var(--gold);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(196,163,90,.3);
  }
  .tl-dot.gold { background: var(--gold); }
  .tl-dot.key { background: var(--red); border-color: var(--red); box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(192,57,43,.4); }
  .tl-era {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px; color: var(--gold); font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 6px; opacity: .8;
  }
  .tl-title { font-weight: 700; color: #fff; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 6px; line-height: 1.4; }
  .tl-body { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.85; }
  .tl-body strong { color: var(--text); }

  /* ── ALERT ── */
  .alert {
    margin: 20px 0; padding: 16px 20px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start;
    font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .alert.gold { background: rgba(196,163,90,.08); border-left: 3px solid var(--gold); color: #e0c07a; }
  .alert.blue { background: rgba(41,128,185,.1); border-left: 3px solid var(--blue); color: #a8d4f0; }
  .alert.red  { background: rgba(192,57,43,.1); border-left: 3px solid var(--red); color: #ffb3a7; }
  .alert.green{ background: rgba(39,174,96,.1); border-left: 3px solid var(--green); color: #a8e0bc; }
  .alert-icon { font-size: 18px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .alert strong { color: inherit; font-weight: 700; }

  /* ── QUOTE ── */
  .quote-block {
    background: #0d0d0d;
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    margin: 20px 0;
    position: relative;
  }
  .quote-mark {
    position: absolute; top: 14px; left: 20px;
    font-size: 48px; color: rgba(196,163,90,.15);
    font-family: Georgia, serif; line-height: 1;
  }
  .quote-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif;
    font-size: 15px; color: rgba(232,224,208,.8);
    line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 16px;
  }
  .quote-src {
    margin-top: 12px; padding-left: 16px;
    font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  /* ── DATA TABLE ── */
  .data-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13.5px; margin: 20px 0; }
  .data-table thead tr { border-bottom: 2px solid var(--line); }
  .data-table thead th {
    padding: 10px 14px; text-align: left;
    font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-muted); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-weight: 500;
  }
  .data-table tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(196,163,90,.07); transition: background .15s; }
  .data-table tbody tr:hover { background: rgba(196,163,90,.04); }
  .data-table tbody td { padding: 12px 14px; vertical-align: top; color: var(--text-dim); }
  .data-table tbody td:first-child { color: var(--text); font-weight: 600; font-size: 13px; }
  .tag { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; }
  .tag-red   { background: rgba(192,57,43,.2); color: #ff8a7a; }
  .tag-gold  { background: rgba(196,163,90,.15); color: var(--gold); }
  .tag-blue  { background: rgba(41,128,185,.15); color: #7ec8f0; }
  .tag-green { background: rgba(39,174,96,.15); color: #6ed99a; }
  .tag-gray  { background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); color: var(--text-muted); }

  /* ── GRID CARDS ── */
  .card-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; margin: 20px 0; }
  .card {
    background: var(--ink-mid);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 4px; padding: 20px 22px;
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 2px; }
  .card.gold::before { background: var(--gold); }
  .card.blue::before { background: var(--blue); }
  .card.red::before  { background: var(--red); }
  .card.green::before{ background: var(--green); }
  .card-label { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .card.gold .card-label { color: var(--gold); }
  .card.blue .card-label { color: #7ec8f0; }
  .card.red  .card-label { color: #ff8a7a; }
  .card.green .card-label { color: #6ed99a; }
  .card-title { font-weight: 700; color: #fff; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.4; }
  .card-body  { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }

  /* ── PHILOSOPHY GRID ── */
  .phil-item {
    display: flex; gap: 20px; align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 20px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .phil-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .phil-num {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(196,163,90,.2); flex-shrink: 0; width: 40px; line-height: 1;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .phil-content {}
  .phil-title { font-weight: 700; color: var(--gold-light); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .phil-body  { font-size: 13.5px; color: var(--text-dim); line-height: 1.85; }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .divider { margin: 48px 0 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }

  /* ── FINAL ── */
  .final-box {
    margin-top: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0a05, #120808);
    border: 1px solid rgba(196,163,90,.2);
    border-radius: 6px; padding: 36px 40px;
  }
  .final-eyebrow { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--gold); text-transform: uppercase; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .final-title { font-family: 'Noto Serif KR', serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 18px; line-height: 1.4; }
  .final-body { font-size: 14.5px; color: rgba(232,224,208,.7); line-height: 1.95; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .final-body strong { color: var(--gold-light); }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 28px 40px;
    font-size: 11px; color: var(--text-muted);
    text-align: center; line-height: 1.8;
  }
  footer a { color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; }

  /* ── MOBILE ── */
  @media(max-width: 640px) {
    header { padding: 40px 20px 36px; }
    .header-inner { flex-direction: column; gap: 28px; }
    .header-portrait { width: 100%; display: flex; gap: 16px; align-items: center; }
    .portrait-frame { width: 80px; height: 100px; font-size: 40px; }
    main { padding: 0 20px 60px; }
    .nav-inner { padding: 0 20px; }
    footer { padding: 24px 20px; }
    .final-box { padding: 28px 24px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══ HEADER ══ -->
<header>
  <div class="header-inner">
    <div class="header-portrait">
      <div class="portrait-frame">🏛️</div>
      <div class="portrait-label">제79대 미국 재무장관</div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-content">
      <div class="brand-row">
        <div class="brand-dot"></div>
        <span class="brand-name">Macro Lens · 인물사전</span>
        <span class="series-badge">Vol. 001</span>
      </div>
      <h1>스콧 베센트</h1>
      <span class="name-en">SCOTT BESSENT · 1962~</span>
      <p class="header-sub">
        소로스 펀드의 수석 투자책임자에서 미국 역사상 최초의 공개적 성소수자 재무장관으로.<br>
        거시경제 투자자에서 달러 패권의 설계자로. 한 인간이 걸어온 63년의 궤적.
      </p>
      <div class="keystats">
        <div class="ks-item">
          <div class="ks-label">출생</div>
          <div class="ks-val">1962 · 사우스캐롤라이나</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ks-item">
          <div class="ks-label">학력</div>
          <div class="ks-val">Yale Univ. 1984</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ks-item">
          <div class="ks-label">현직</div>
          <div class="ks-val">미 재무장관 (2025~)</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ks-item">
          <div class="ks-label">전직</div>
          <div class="ks-val">Soros Fund CIO</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ks-item">
          <div class="ks-label">투자 스타일</div>
          <div class="ks-val">글로벌 매크로</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ══ NAV ══ -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a class="nav-tab active" href="#early">유년 · 성장</a>
